Package ca.openosp.openo.rx.erx.model.request

Class SetPatientImmediate3

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.rx.erx.model.request.SetPatientImmediate3
public class SetPatientImmediate3 extends Object
Provides an interface for the the External Prescriber SetPatientImmediate3 method, which must be called by sending a SOAP request to the External Prescriber's www service.
See Also:
  • The the External Prescriber SetPatientImmediate3 www service demo page

      transaction - A transaction object to pass in the request.
      patient - The patient data to send.
